{"tid":238541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老老豆豆，如果條女因為呢啲言論而自殺，你良心過意唔去","createTime":"2017-05-11T05:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T05:29:43.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c8452561b0f5f169e15b0e5aa48a44f34ffe079","tid":238541,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:29:44.000Z","msg":"成班又係度講好似鳩噏當秘笈<br />\n以為自己講嘢唔使負責，仲好好笑添<br />\n費事又話口德撚同你地嘈<br />\n回帶最實際<br />\n<br />\n我想今個星期六等屋企人出曬街之後跳樓<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/87086/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/87086/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得呢單野，大把人留言叫佢去死。點知嗰晚新聞出街話真係有個40幾歲嘅人死，成班就嚇到瀨屎咁，不停叫樓主上水。雖然證實左爸打冇自殺，但係都睇到成班友驚佢自殺以為佢夜麻麻會搵你咁。如果條女真係因為呢啲言論而自殺，你哋咩嚇到瀨屎咁嘅樣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}